text: Compared to East Coast Park, it is relatively quiet and you can enjoy the sea in a calm atmosphere.You can also see the approach of landing planes.
Becareful of stonefish . Stepping on one is life threatening. Beachgoers beware by Adib .

quiet relaxing portion of east coast park. the trees and grass here are abundant and green. Beach is clean and less crowded. Area can be pleasantly dark at night however the path is well illuminated by light posts. I frequent this place currently for what it is.
Excellent location for cycling, Sailing and clean beach
